        {
            "id": 6097918,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 堤維西(1522)大跌7.52%，報39.35元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>堤維西(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1522-TW</a>)08日09:00股價下跌3.2元，報39.35元，跌幅7.52%，成交278張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>堤維西(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1522-TW</a>)所屬產業為汽車工業，主要業務為汽車燈。機車燈。汽車百貨及零件。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.29%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.96%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,351 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,352 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-11 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+10 張</li> <li>融資增減：-81 張</li> <li>融券增減：+249 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6097918",
